X:1
T:SPECTRAL Test - Velocity-Dependent Timbre
M:4/4
L:1/4
Q:1/4=100
K:C
%%SPECTRAL tilt 0.2
%%SPECTRAL cc 74 0.5
%%SPECTRAL cc 71 0.3
%
% Ascending dynamics — louder notes should get brighter (higher CC74)
% and slightly sharper (pitch bend up)
!pp! C D E F | !mp! G A B c | !f! d e f g | !ff! a b c' d' |
%
% Descending — quieter = warmer, flatter
!ff! d' c' b a | !f! g f e d | !mp! c B A G | !pp! F E D C |
%
% Turn off — should stop emitting CC and pitch bend
%%SPECTRAL off
!pp! C D E F | !ff! G A B c |]
